{{ZScriptNote}} '''[[Structs:SecPlane|SecPlane]]'''
native bool '''isEqual'''(SecPlane ''other'') const
==Usage== Checks if the given SecPlane is equal to the calling one.
===Parameters=== *''other'' - The SecPlane to check against.
===Return Value=== Returns true if the two SecPlanes are the same.
==Examples== {{noexamples}}
